comments: I have Dr. Gatewood at NDM, and he is horrible. Changed the course outline beyond recognition, gave us a 30 page research paper to write in 2 weeks, NEVER responds to emails.

Required writing a full semester Masters Thesis in 11 weeks. Not enough availability or feedback. Really really too stuck on his outline and keeping it up to date for you to even research and write the paper. Just seemed doomed from the start.
does not cover enough materails in the book to justify midterm very lousy with explaining chapters to fully understand.
